<task id="GUID-BED80320-70E5-47C4-9530-CC26073D469D" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title id="GUID-71E6E7FF-D420-465A-9CFA-86F8BA5BE094">Application Lockdown</title>
    <taskbody>
        <context>
            <p>When Application Lockdown is turned on, the agent will only be able to access
                applications that are in the Approved List. </p>
        </context>
        <steps id="steps_hgj_l3v_35b">
            <step>
                <cmd>Go to <menucascade>
                        <uicontrol>Agents</uicontrol>
                        <uicontrol>All</uicontrol>
                    </menucascade>.</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd><ph conkeyref="PRODvars/POLICY"/></cmd>
                <info>
                    <note id="note_kqb_dvc_jvb">
                        <p><ph conkeyref="PRODvars/POLICY_NOTE"/></p>
                    </note>
                </info>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Go to the <uicontrol>Application Lockdown</uicontrol> section.</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Three modes are avaible for selection:</cmd>
                <info>
                    <ul id="ul_yww_l2h_55b">
                        <li>
                            <p>Detect: When an application not in the Approved List launches, it is
                                allowed and users will receive a notification.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p>Enforce: When an application not in the Approved List launches, it is
                                blocked and users will receive a notification.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p>Disable: Application Lockdown is turned off.</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <note id="note_tdv_b5v_35b">
                        <p>For how to configure exclusion settings for the Approved List, please
                            refer to the <xref href="lockdownExclusions=20220729170241.xml">Lockdown
                                Exclusions</xref>.</p>
                    </note>
                </info>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task>
